text: Des Moines is a city in Iowa. It is the capital city of Iowa. The city had a population of 214,133 in the 2020 United States Census. It is the home of the Des Moines Art Center, a regional art museum, and the Pappajohn Sculpture Park, an outdoor sculpture garden. == References == Category:County seats in Iowa Category:State capitals in the United States
title: Des Moines, Iowa
